Trigger an astounding star wipe page-load transition, navigating to the specified url upon completion (note: only works in the latest WebKit browsers).
Add an astounding star wipe page-load transition to the click event on one or more elements, optionally specifying a URL to navigate to (note: only works in the latest WebKit browsers).
